Uses of Package
net.myorb.math

  • Packages that use net.myorb.math 
    Package Description
    net.myorb.junit
    JUnit test suite for CalcLib primitive layer.
    net.myorb.math
    Primitive data structure layer and implementation of arithmetic at lowest levels.
    net.myorb.math.characteristics
    Eigenvalue and eigenvector primitive descriptions and implementations.
    net.myorb.math.complexnumbers
    Implementations of functionality supporting complex number fields.
    net.myorb.math.computational
    Support for computation in multiple dimensions mostly focused on calculus.
    net.myorb.math.expressions
    Core set of classes supporting representation of expressions and their evaluations.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.algorithms
    Implementations of algorithms that provide for evaluation of expression primitives.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.charting
    Implementations of the charting interface that provide a default charting solution.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.charting.fractals
    Implementations of algorithms that compute plot data for fractals.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.controls
    Control layer for the CalcLib application including selection of the base type for a run.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.evaluationstates
    Primitive abstract data layer for the CalcLib environment including functions and operators.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.managers
    Implementation of the Space Management interface for the supported data types (Integer, Real, Complex).
    net.myorb.math.expressions.symbols
    Support for symbols declared in the CalcLib environment including data and operator definitions.
    net.myorb.math.expressions.tree
    Definition of the expression tree that provides efficient execution of evaluation and static storage of expressions as JSON source.
    net.myorb.math.fractions
    Abstract representation for fractions and algoriths for fraction arithmetic.
    net.myorb.math.linalg
    Linear Algebra algorithm implementations for solutions to equation sets.
    net.myorb.math.matrices
    Representations for Vectors and Matricies and implementations of their arithmetic operators.
    net.myorb.math.matrices.decomposition
    Implementations of matrix decomposition algorithms.
    net.myorb.math.matrices.optimization
    Implementations of algorithms supporting efficient computation of Matrix cofactors.
    net.myorb.math.matrices.transforms
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Householder and Von Mises transforms.
    net.myorb.math.polynomial
    Implementations of algorithms supporting polynomial concepts (family, calculus, fields).
    net.myorb.math.polynomial.families
    Implementations of algorithms supporting polynomial families (Hermits, Jacobi, Legendre, others).
    net.myorb.math.polynomial.families.bessel
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Bessel polynomial family specifically.
    net.myorb.math.polynomial.families.chebyshev
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Chebyshev polynomial family specifically.
    net.myorb.math.polynomial.families.gegenbauer
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Gegenbauer polynomial family specifically.
    net.myorb.math.polynomial.families.jacobi
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Jacobi polynomial family specifically.
    net.myorb.math.polynomial.families.legendre
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Legendre polynomial family specifically.
    net.myorb.math.primenumbers
    Implementations of algorithms supporting prime number use and factorization in particular.
    net.myorb.math.realnumbers
    Implementations of space management interface for real number fields.
    net.myorb.math.specialfunctions
    Implementations of algorithms supporting special functions (Bessel, Gamma, Ei, other).
    net.myorb.math.specialfunctions.bessel
    Implementations of algorithms supporting Bessel special functions specifically.
    net.myorb.math.vanche
    Data representations supporting implementation of VanChe linear algebra concepts.
    net.myorb.testing
    Implementations of algorithms supporting CalcLib unit tests.
    net.myorb.testing.anal  
    net.myorb.testing.splines  
    net.myorb.testing.squareRoot  
    net.myorb.testing.vc31
